query:
DELETE FROM events 
WHERE name = 'Breakfast Meeting' 
AND id IN (
  SELECT e.id 
  FROM events e 
  LEFT JOIN participants p ON e.id = p.eventId 
  WHERE e.name = 'Breakfast Meeting' 
  GROUP BY e.id 
  HAVING COUNT(p.id) = 0
);
